articles.author: Matt Kew
articles.title: Aston Martin: Stroll crash shows F1 commitment, not recklessness - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Lance Stroll's major Singapore qualifying crash that led him to withdraw from the race proves doubters wrong and underlines his commitment, says Aston Martin  Formula 1 team boss Mike Krack.
articles.content: Stroll felt as though his final flying lap in Q1 had been heavily disrupted by poor tyre preparation, traffic and dirty air. That prompted the Canadian to 'send it' into the final corners at Marina B… [+2324 chars]
